description: Try our easy to follow Teriyaki Beef Stir-Fry Noodles recipe. Absolutely delicious with the best ingredients from Woolworths.
name: Teriyaki Beef Stir-Fry Noodles Recipe | Woolworths

recipeInstructions.text: Add noodles and sauce, then cook, stirring, 4 minutes or until heated through. Add vegetables and cook, tossing, for 1 minute or until wilted. Divide stir-fry among bowls. Serve topped with cashew crumble.
